al tally\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"9.784 seconds\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"Thompson\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The new champion said that before he left for Paris, one of his physio guys ensured him this race would be a squeaker.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5454203655647467e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The new champion\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"his physio guys\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 993}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"a squeaker\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He said, 'This is how close first and second are going to be,'\\\" Lyles said as he pinched his thumb and his forefinger together so they were almost touching.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"his thumb\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"his forefinger\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not believe how right he was.\\\"\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For perspective, the blink of an eye takes, on average, .1 second.\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"perspective\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"the blink\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"an eye\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was 20 times longer than the gap between first and second.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was so close, that when the sprinters crossed the line and the word \\\"Photo\\\" popped up next to the names of Lyles, Thompson and five others in the eight-man field, Lyles walked over to the Jamaican and said \\\"I think you got the Olympics dog.\\\"\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9962146911447616, \"rank\": 0.003799540493677415, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1484, \"end\": 1492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9994585873094793, \"rank\": 0.000541705976980802, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9962146911447616, \"rank\": 0.003799540493677415, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1558, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.8047906836614217, \"rank\": 0.24255911543197536, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sprinters\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1424}, {\"ngram\": \"the word\", \"from\": 1429, \"t