ll.\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Time\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It always does.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Lyles' name came up first, he snatched his name tag off the front of his bib and held it to the sky.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles' name\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"his name tag\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"his bib\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moments later, he shouted at the TV camera: \\\"America, I told you I got this!\\\"\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the TV camera\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first four racers were separated by less than .03.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first four racers\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top seven all finished within .09 of each other.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"America's Fred Kerley came in third at 9.81.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's probably one of the most beautiful races I have been in,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most beautiful races\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the photo finish, Kerley's orange shoe crossed the line before anyone, or anything.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the photo finish\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerley's orange shoe\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's the chest breaking the barrier that counts.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chest\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"the barrier\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles' chest crossed first.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles' chest\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the closest 1-2 finish in the 100 since at least Moscow in 1980 - or maybe even ever.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4107094937665136e-14, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closest 1-2 finish\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back then, Britain's Allan Wells narrowly beat Silvio Leonard in an era when the electronic timers did not go into the thousandths of a second.\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9982411570977016, \"rank\": 0.0017619300937497474, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allan_Wells\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allan Wells\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allan_Wells\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allan_Wells\"}, {\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvio_Leonard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Silvio Leonard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvio_Leonard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silvio_Leonard\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an era\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"the electronic timers\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"the thousandths\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same was true in 1932, when Eddie Tolan won the Olympics' first ever photo finish.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Tolan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eddie Tolan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Tolan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eddie_Tolan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics' first ever photo finish\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles conceded that during the excruciating wait, he was pretty sure he had dipped his chest just a tad too soon.\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"the excruciating wait\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"his chest\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dipping, it turns out, is one of the few things he does not work on over and over again at his training track in Florida.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2983, \"end\": 2990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.797080390638658, \"rank\": 0.2539687643228627, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the few things\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"his training track\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I would say I have a decent history with dipping,\\\" he said, recalling races he won in high school and as a junior.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decent history\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"dipping\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"a junior\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 9.784 marked a new personal best for Lyles and made him the first American champion in the marquee race at the Olympics since Justin Gatlin in 2004.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3155, \"end\": 3160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9962146911447616, \"rank\": 0.003799540493677415, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3244, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Gatlin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Gatlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Gatlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Gatlin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the marquee race\", \"from\": 32