 also looked for a new mission - the 100 meters and, with it, a chance at track immortality.\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mental health\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"a new mission\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3810}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100 meters\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3827}, {\"ngram\": \"track immortality\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The practice was tough for a sprinter never known as a great starter, but he stuck with it.\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3965, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The practice\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3886}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprinter\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3911}, {\"ngram\": \"a great starter\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he won the world championships last year, then backed it up by winning the 200, his goal for Paris was very much in sight.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4064, \"end\": 4069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5454203655647467e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 3978, \"to\": 4001}, {\"ngram\": \"his goal\", \"from\": 4051, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 4087, \"to\": 4092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when he came into the Olympic final having finished second in both his qualifying races and staring across at one sprinter who had run faster than him this year - Thompson - and another who had beaten him twice this year - Jamaica's Oblique Seville - he knew this would be no coronation.\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4322, \"end\": 4329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.9136298468299497e-12, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"